= SDL_JoystickAttachVirtual =

Attach a new virtual joystick.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int SDL_JoystickAttachVirtual(SDL_JoystickType type,
                              int naxes,
                              int nbuttons,
                              int nhats);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Return Value ==

Returns the joystick's device index, or -1 if an error occurred.


